706838f-b.title: Brooklyn: Stagg Street - Union Avenue
706838f-b.text:
Stagg Street, east of Union Ave., showing along the south side of
Btagg Street, the demolition of homes which are to be replaced by modern
(F.H.A.) apartments.
September 27, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
4. S.f. corner ofStagg St. A Union Ave., B'klyn.
Sept. 24, 1941
P.L. Sperr, photographer
